-- NAB, IOOF Holdings Close to North Platform Deal, Financial Review Reports
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-07-01T21:14:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/nab-ioof-holdings-close-to-north-platform-deal-financial-review-reports.html

          
          
             National Australia Bank Ltd. and IOOF
Holdings Ltd. are close to signing a three to five year pact for
the management of funds on Axa Asia Pacific Holdings Ltd.’s
North platform, the Australian Financial Review reported in its
Street Talk column, without saying where it got the information.
IOOF may manage the North platform’s A$1.2 billion in funds
under management on behalf of National Australia in return for a
fee, according to the report.  
